en_815081_0	54 Division troops of the SFHQ-Wanni, ahead of the Maha Shivarathri Day conducted a Shramadana campaign and cleaned the Thiruketheswarn Kovil premises on Friday (1).
en_815081_1	The Shramadana campaign was launched under the supervision of the General Officer Commanding 54 Division, Brigadier Senarath Bandara.
en_815081_2	05 Officers and 85 other ranks participated in the Shramadana campaign.
en_815081_3	It was continued throughout the day .The Secretary and the Kovil Committee extended their gratitude to the troops for the enormous support given to them.
